{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":227492,"originalJapaneseLine":"　体に異常なし」","translatedEnglishLine":"'No abnormalities in the body.'"},{"lineNumber":227493,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちっ、くっだらねー魔法を使いやがって」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Tch, using such stupid magic.'"},

{"lineNumber":227494,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しっかし、あれだな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'But still, that is...'"},

{"lineNumber":227495,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん？　どした？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hmm? What's up?'"},

{"lineNumber":227496,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぎゃーーっはっはっはっはっ！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Gyaaa-hahahahaha!'"},

{"lineNumber":227497,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんだぁ、テメェ！　その姿は！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'What the hell, you! That appearance!'"},

{"lineNumber":227498,"originalJapaneseLine":"「は！　腹痛ぇ！　ぎゃはははははははは！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Ha! My stomach hurts! Gahahahahaha!'"},

{"lineNumber":227499,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ふ、普通のハニーの筈なのに笑える！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Huh, it's supposed to be a normal Hanny but it's laughable!'"},

{"lineNumber":227500,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くきーーーっ！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Kukiiiii!'"},

{"lineNumber":227501,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんだお前ー！　笑うなー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'What the hell are you! Don't laugh!'"},

{"lineNumber":227502,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そのナリ見て笑うなとか無理言うんじゃねぇよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Don't tell me it's impossible not to laugh when looking at how you look!'"},

{"lineNumber":227503,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ぎゃはははははは！　げーほっ！　げほっ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Gahahahaha! *cough* *cough*'"},

{"lineNumber":227504,"originalJapaneseLine":"「咳き込むくらい笑うなー！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Don't laugh so hard you start coughing!'"},

{"lineNumber":227505,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うわーん！　乱義ー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Wahhh! Rangii!'"},

{"lineNumber":227506,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"'............'"},

{"lineNumber":227507,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふぐっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Fugu...'"},

{"lineNumber":227508,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今笑わなかった！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Did you just not laugh now?!'"},

{"lineNumber":227509,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや……大丈夫……す、すまない……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'No... I'm okay... s-sorry...'"},

{"lineNumber":227510,"originalJapaneseLine":"乱義は顔を背けて肩をプルプル震わせていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Rangii turned his face away and his shoulders trembled."},

{"lineNumber":227511,"originalJapaneseLine":"「大丈夫ならこっち向けー！","translatedEnglishLine":"'If you're okay, look this way!'"},

{"lineNumber":227512,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うわーん！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Wahhh!'"},

{"lineNumber":227513,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ヒーッ、腹いてー……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hee, my stomach hurts...'"},

{"lineNumber":227514,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ところでザンス！　乱義！","translatedEnglishLine":"'By the way, Zansu! Rangii!'"},

{"lineNumber":227515,"originalJapaneseLine":"　オレ達の服はどこ行った！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Where did our clothes go?!'"},

{"lineNumber":227516,"originalJapaneseLine":"「テメェは……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'You...'"},

{"lineNumber":227517,"originalJapaneseLine":"「少しは話を聞きなさい……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Listen to what I'm saying a little...'"},

{"lineNumber":227518,"originalJapaneseLine":"自分の前で行われる兄達の会話を、","translatedEnglishLine":"The conversation between the older brothers taking place before her,"},

{"lineNumber":227519,"originalJapaneseLine":"スシヌは不思議そうに聞いていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Sushinu listened with curiosity."},

{"lineNumber":227520,"originalJapaneseLine":"（み、みんなすごいなぁ……","translatedEnglishLine":"(E-everyone's amazing..."},

{"lineNumber":227521,"originalJapaneseLine":"　裸なのに……もうすっかりいつも通りで……）","translatedEnglishLine":"...even though they're naked... they're already just like usual...)"},

{"lineNumber":227522,"originalJapaneseLine":"（た、確かに子供の頃は","translatedEnglishLine":"(I-I do remember that when we were kids,"},

{"lineNumber":227523,"originalJapaneseLine":"　一緒にお風呂に入ったことも","translatedEnglishLine":"we used to bathe together often,"},

{"lineNumber":227524,"originalJapaneseLine":"　しょっちゅうあったけど……）","translatedEnglishLine":"quite frequently though...)"},

{"lineNumber":227525,"originalJapaneseLine":"（男の子と女の子の差？）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Is it the difference between boys and girls?)"},

{"lineNumber":227526,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そういえば、ミックスちゃんは――」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Speaking of which, Mix-chan—'"},

{"lineNumber":227527,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こら待て、なんで皆揃って、","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hey, wait, why does everyone,"},

{"lineNumber":227528,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あたしをちゃん付けするわけ」","translatedEnglishLine":"'address me with '-chan' all together?'"},

{"lineNumber":227529,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うーん、それはもう、","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hmm, well that's because,'"},

{"lineNumber":227530,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ミックス！　ってよりは","translatedEnglishLine":"'more than calling you Mix!'"},

{"lineNumber":227531,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ミックスちゃん！　って感じだからでは？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'it's more the feeling of Mix-chan!'"},

{"lineNumber":227532,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……クソが」","translatedEnglishLine":"'...Damn it.'"},

{"lineNumber":227533,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ミックスちゃん、口悪いでござるなぁ」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Mix-chan, you have a foul mouth, don't you?'"},

{"lineNumber":227534,"originalJapaneseLine":"同性のウズメ達も大して気にしていなかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"Uzume and the other girls of the same sex didn't really care."},

{"lineNumber":227535,"originalJapaneseLine":"（うう……関係ないよね……","translatedEnglishLine":"(Ugh... it doesn't matter, right...)"},

{"lineNumber":227536,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こんなに恥ずかしがってるの私だけだよね……）","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm the only one embarrassed like this, right...)"},

{"lineNumber":227537,"originalJapaneseLine":"（ふ、普通にしていた方がいいのかな……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Huh, maybe I should just act normal...)"},

{"lineNumber":227538,"originalJapaneseLine":"試しにと体を隠していた両腕を","translatedEnglishLine":"As a test, she gently lowered her arms that had been hiding her body,"},

{"lineNumber":227539,"originalJapaneseLine":"そっと下ろして肌を晒してみた。","translatedEnglishLine":"exposing her skin."},

{"lineNumber":227540,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Ah...'"},

{"lineNumber":227541,"originalJapaneseLine":"カーーーッと一気に顔が赤く染まる。","translatedEnglishLine":"Her face instantly flushed bright red."},

{"lineNumber":227542,"originalJapaneseLine":"（無理無理無理無理無理！","translatedEnglishLine":"(No way no way no way no way no way!"},

{"lineNumber":227543,"originalJapaneseLine":"　絶対、無理ーーーーー！）","translatedEnglishLine":"Absolutely impossible------!)"},

{"lineNumber":227544,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あんた……何、百面相してんの？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'You... what kind of faces are you making?'"},

{"lineNumber":227545,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うう、ごめん……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Ugh, sorry...'"},

{"lineNumber":227546,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……はあ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'...Huh?'"},

{"lineNumber":227547,"originalJapaneseLine":"（というか……","translatedEnglishLine":"(Or rather..."},

{"lineNumber":227548,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こんなにあれこれ考えてるの、","translatedEnglishLine":"Am I the only one thinking about all this?"},

{"lineNumber":227549,"originalJapaneseLine":"　もしかして私だけ……？）","translatedEnglishLine":"Maybe I'm the only one...?)"},

{"lineNumber":227550,"originalJapaneseLine":"（…………）","translatedEnglishLine":"(........)"},

{"lineNumber":227551,"originalJapaneseLine":"（うう、私って……情けないなぁ……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Ugh, I really am... pitiful...)"}
]}
